edia.org/resource/Iowa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And whether we like it or not, water quality that discourages swimming, kayaking and fishing are activities that should concern people who call this state home or who come to visit us.\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Or, it should.\", \"from\": 3364, \"to\": 3378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2666  Randy Evans can be reached atDMRevans2810@gmail.com.\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3382, \"end\": 3393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999985100591589, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Randy Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your email address will not be published.Required fields are marked*  Comment*  Name*  Email*  Website  Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment.\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u0394\", \"from\": 3623, \"to\": 3624, \"entities\": []}]}"